articles.author: NBCNews.com
articles.title: Americans evacuated from quarantined cruise ship off Japan
articles.description: Hundreds of Americans are being evacuated off the Diamond Princess for a chartered flight back to the United States, where they’ll face a 14-day quarantine. There are 355 confirmed coronavirus cases on the ship and the number could rise as more people onboard…

articles.author: NBC News
articles.title: Coronavirus: Americans to be evacuated from cruise ship quarantined in Japan
articles.description: As the U.S. prepares to evacuate passengers from the quarantined Diamond Princess cruise ship in Japan, China confirmed the coronavirus death toll has risen.
